unavailable.reason_english: There was not enough data to publish information specifically for this course. This is either because the course size is small or not enough students responded to a survey. For this reason, the data displayed is for all students in Animal science.
unavailable.reason_welsh: Nid oedd digon o ddata ar gael i gyhoeddi gwybodaeth yn benodol ar gyfer y cwrs hwn. Mae hyn naill ai oherwydd bod maint y cwrs yn fach neu am nad ymatebodd digon o fyfyrwyr i arolwg. Am y rheswm hwn, mae'r data a ddangosir ar gyfer yr holl fyfyrwyr mewn Gwyddorau anifeiliaid.
